      "message": "Mostly. For these invalid load increments, the intent is that it is only called for valid snapshot PB data that nonetheless resulted in a failed snapshot for some reason (crash or failure to load for some other reason). It is possible to set version earlier though if the emulator crashes before the snapshot PB data was ever created. But in that case, we would just end up creating a PB file whose only purpose is to force a cold boot next emulator start.",
